criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  adults aged 50 years or over;

          -  Community-dweller;

          -  independent to be standing and walking, with or without walking aids;

          -  interest to participate in the study.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  individuals with severe sensorial impairments (deafness or blindness)

          -  individuals with cognitive impairments which precludes the ability to comprehend the
             questionnaire, functional tests and exercises included in the protocol.
